data.description: Welcome to your new home! This one story 4 bedroom home located on a Cul-De-Sac is a family’s dream come true! This open  floor plan home is perfect for those who love to entertain. Come enjoy the outdoor oasis of a back yard. Just think of all the memories that will be made poolside on those hot summer day's with family and friends. So many updates have been done.  New roof, fresh paint just to name a few. All buyers must be pre-approved and the pre-approval must be submitted with any offer. Contact the listing agent for additional information.
